headline: Does General Dynamics Still Have Room to Run After Pentagon Push for Higher Missile Output?
summary: If you have been tracking defense stocks or holding General Dynamics for a while, you probably know it has sparked fresh debates among investors about what the future holds. With shares closing at $331.15 and that impressive 26.9% rally so far this year, it is only natural to wonder whether there is still room to run or if the price has already baked in all the good news.
